jishoData.meaning: sign of the dog, 7-9PM, eleventh sign of Chinese zodiac

onyomiExamples.meaning: Fire Dog (23rd term of the sexagenary cycle, e.g. 1946, 2006, 2066)
Wood Dog (11th term of the sexagenary cycle, e.g. 1934, 1994, 2054)

kunyomiExamples.meaning: the Dog (eleventh sign of the Chinese zodiac), hour of the Dog (around 8pm, 7-9pm, or 8-10pm), west-northwest, ninth month of the lunar calendar
Metal Dog (47th term of the sexagenary cycle, e.g. 1910, 1970, 2030)
Wood Dog (11th term of the sexagenary cycle, e.g. 1934, 1994, 2054)
